  "title": "Dental Nurse #82140",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Healthcare (Dental Services)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Dental Nurse</strong></li><li>Working Location: Novena (6-minute walking distance from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri, 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM; Sat, 8:30 AM – 1:00 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + VB + OT</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist the dentist during procedures, ensuring a smooth and efficient workflow.</li><li>Prepare and sterilize dental instruments and equipment according to standards.</li><li>Take and process dental X-rays as required.</li><li>Maintain patient records accurately and update them as needed.</li><li>Manage patient appointments and assist with scheduling at the front desk.</li><li>Handle patient inquiries and provide excellent customer service.</li><li>Ensure a clean and organized dental environment.</li><li>Follow infection control and safety procedures.</li><li>Assist in front desk operations, including patient check-in, billing, and insurance processing.</li><li>Coordinate with other healthcare providers to ensure optimal patient care.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of experience as a Nurse with front desk duties.</li><li>Diploma in Dental Nursing or equivalent.</li><li>Knowledge of dental procedures, instruments, sterilization protocols, and dental software.</li><li>Strong communication, organizational, and multitasking skills.</li><li>Ability to provide excellent patient care in a fast-paced environment</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82140 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
